[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating Jakarta activation API**\n\nI'm diving into some details about the Jakarta activation API and the POM. It seems the API jar just has definitions and doesn't include implementation specifics. I need to think about whether it requires an extra dependency, like com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation. \n\nI'm also considering that while the working classes are there, certain implementations, like CommandMap, might reference classes that could lead to runtime errors if not present. I'll inspect the MailcapCommandMap and its constant pool for more insights.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_00954c5f3a6cd94b016a41bb4f95148195aa176fc28a36c115\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQbtThNdh-YpH7gqepuqZeR-gXZ-4gaWEOrnYFqtFqsYWxsSqMaBSpXtuCD2dx-hzas7XO9zDHSdd87rpdaBV3RXd9y3rsP68uySmFgTMihKbi844vS2RmIP_xPyBFzbuas0WoI3vESMmJ1lu9PAO_OoOXvBamVQCv0fWTGrFQBT7sMAfx9NcMbZ_iUOQK_AK4dGIdT1WUTJWStMHoP2E6yzEZMGMEPveY2PGBIhjB0Wq8Pz9vO22z6tiSBnF_qe1pfc1QBEKQYanAjqqO8aHbxIQH6fxngL2DJbr5QvLJmcgWEdYbnLSBSPGgp9F9bs2C8lxpfyfhcfjstCQb_9HJPNlyYI-eYz1NrOMCj5si3aAsbB6C1AzE55pNaeXwS27OySmoQzCiCRWeiycJwXCWGQQO-nYbhWR98s73ndWPYxGeNiulp5RuPQQIZ50FEbbjzyMX3DtRtCyi6Du8sdGrIAgQwYkK7g8kT_1sgQyFL2BbL3z_Js11f90_XsQWDTMZ76C3HB0XbdUa9h8EHgiNd8nUVCKmHbmE9aUA8xR23d2afzRl_eV6Ck8Gu9F1C1lToLOkZ0a8PpGvic7xV_5lETfuTZJvEKcGbfLrKMrn2jRcawhoGoLXZnj9UyknfrBKkL7y8YoIZ-abtKzTdde7G2pOCPTfotwiiiJs8JliRvwn9yq4E1uqIn2WKiEfG36vUkDzOrFQoLCjo2BefJqnrTnkFQ1s7D2WcIkVY8LA6dswtTXdDjFqGgdcVa7pmBfXDIMntCYIR0-HDCRI9qBQ71C-5xcp0EDwxR3qdiCGt59JEG4-iph6CQnh9PIGGlEZMYeFCMOirhw2HOeRuRiNzpF9MMJ_JZRKthTQZ7BczPYzRbOrdYaFLB3dVFQCTWWsEu8FBq-lmy-VnAKqivzvg3wftoK0ZHKfc_RRkKZapGbldzalWlnZGxNNv-lo2u9XaF8oRiWWtXa_KTMEFX03wCRVwQSwqa_qwnLNYLQ85SSPGJ7-4aHOp86qnDb6Xys01-3M7ws4cZ4HmPHWI5ol42KVligKCoeBAvzvbyeoFImMPosSmSZWqMG4VnwPNEjq8fMB-cgIRRtSFepkW7OWbN63NWUPi1Kh8J2B2-jMKOwDBKfXZ7YRyKMAAWMMOyTqKC4LqK2