 implementation-specific classes, while runtime paths such as command and MIME mapping reference implementation classes under com.sun.activation.registries.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation:2.0.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Provides the implementation-specific registry classes and default activation resources needed to exercise MailcapCommandMap, MimetypesFileTypeMap, content-handler lookup, and normal Jakarta Activation runtime behavior for version 2.0.0.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For Jakarta Activation 2.0.0 tests, use the `jakarta.activation.*` package and reflection names such as `jakarta.activation.SecuritySupport`; do not carry forward old `javax.activation.*` imports from the 1.2.1 tests.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The implementation artifact also contains the jakarta.activation API classes, so the test classpath will contain duplicate API classes; local Gradle and Native Image verification should remain authoritative.\",\n    \"If tests only cover compile-only API paths such as simple CommandInfo construction, the extra implementation may not be strictly necessary, but it is needed for normal activation runtime coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00954c5f3a6cd94b016a41bb90689c8195a476b60d6efbf327\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 7047, "output": 1204, "cacheRead": 26624, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34875, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782692736177, "responseId": "resp_00954c5f3a6cd94b016a41bb80c18c8195b002ec03e9dc37a7"}}
